task.summary: Default task
Added prototype code to parse out the field summary.
Changed tack, I'm going to use the existing documentation structure after all. Found some good code for a basic browser that I can extend.
Added Search functionality and forward/back buttons.
Made it possible to browse all the docs, not just the classes.
Split JReader class into JReaderPanel and JReader.
Got tabbed panes working
Changed to RSyntaxPane for the syntax highlighting.
Added JReaderSetup class to handle setting everything up on first launch.
Added methods to create new JReader and JSource tabs.
Removed dead code.
Added hacky functionality to load class source code in JSourcePane tab.
Added class to download files from the net.
Added cancel option to download. Added download and extract methods to JReaderSetup.
Fixed some bugs with incorrect paths getting passed to JSourcePane. Added experimental code folding/expanding methods. Added some comments.
Added more comments.
Fixed bug with passing a url that begins with file:// to Paths.get(url).toUri on Linux.
Added new class PathData to deal with converting paths from documentation to source and handle extracting method/constant information.
Fixed some more issues with paths on Windows.
Made it possible to clear the textField.
Clear the searchBar after a search in JReaderPanel.
Removed redundant code.
Added check to prevent error when user is browsing with frames enabled.
Put PathData class into its own file.
Refactored documentation parsing to separate logic from display.
Changed how the docs are parsed to extract more information about methods and constructors. Got rid of the JavaClassData object and replaced it with JavaObject.
Used JavaScript for back and forward.
Fixed bug in JavaDocParser that caused it to fail to parse lots of methods and fields.
Fixed bug that prevented content being rendered on startup.
Removed some unneeded code from newSourceTab
Made tab titles display current page.
Added prototype menu.
Removed PathData class.
Refactor FileDownloader to use ProgressWindow.
Add new FileDownloaderProgressWindow to JReaderSetup.
Add actions for closing and opening new tab.
Add progress bar to zip extraction.
Fix some bugs with file paths.
Change from Properties to Preferences api for managing configuration.
Add Find menu.
Testing if a singleton will work with the Preference API on windows.
Used Intellij's inspection.
Integrated new Parser.
Fixed some bugs with incorrect paths.
Fixed bug where broken up method or constructor names would non be found in JSourcePanel.
Partially implemented profiles. Changed back to Properties API from the Preferences API.
Added Setup window.
Improved Profile menu and cleaned up JReader constructor.
Fixed bug where it was possible to save a profile with invalid filename.
Fixed issue where menus weren't updating correctly when profiles were added or deleted.
Fixed issue where JavaSourceFileParser didn't find declarations in nested classes.
